<p>Losing a friend is a profound experience, and reaching out with empathy is crucial.  These messages aim to offer support and understanding to a friend navigating grief.</p>
<li>I'm so incredibly sorry for your loss. My heart aches for you.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending all my love during this difficult time.</li>
<li>I can't imagine what you're going through. Please know I'm here for you.</li>
<li>Your friend was a truly special person, and I'll miss them dearly.</li>
<li>Let me know if there's anything at all I can do to help.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you grieve.</li>
<li> Remembering your friend with fondness and warmth.</li>
<li> I am here for you, whatever you need.  </li>
